{
  "texts": [
    "(left) The standard surface code with physical qubits on the vertices of a square lattice and standard Pauli-X and Pauli-Z type stabilizers marked by lattice faces.",
    "Supports for the logical Pauli-X and Pauli-Z operators are shown in green and blue, respectively.",
    "(right) We show the initial state that is injected into the surface code.",
    "The [[4, 1, 2]] code is shown in red in the bottom-left corner.",
    "The remaining qubits of the surface code lattice are prepared in a product state, where blue (green) qubits are prepared in the |0 v ( + v |) state."
  ]
}